  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Perfectly located in the heart of the old village of Val d’Isère and close to the Solaise lift, the recently refurbished Hotel Ormelune is a delight for the senses. Decorated in an imaginative and contemporary style, you’ll be welcomed by the friendly staff as well as numerous brightly-coloured cows and sheep! The hotel is named after the beautiful Ormelune peak, close to Val d’Isère on the French/Italian border. The lounge and bar area are a popular place to enjoy a drink in the evening, with plenty of games on hand for children and the sauna and hammam provide much-needed relaxation at the end of the day.</span></p>]]></description>
