  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Twin bedrooms are modern, bright and comfortable with a shower and village view.</li>
<li>All rooms have TV, telephone, hairdryer, safe and Wi-Fi.</li>
<li>Rooms with a bath are available at a supplement on request.</li>
<li>Larger twin rooms with a south facing balcony can take an extra bed for a child.</li>
<li>Family suites have a double bedroom, living room and cabin with bunk beds for 2 children up to 12 yrs and are on request.</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
